      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Spokane newsboys have enlisted\nto aid in the fight for free speech.\nAt meeting of the Industrial\nNewsboys' association, held Sunday\nnight, resolutions of sympathy were\nadopted and the support of the boys\npledged in the fight. The follow\ning resolutions were adopted:\n\n\nWhereas, The constitution of\nthe United States guarantees us\nthe right of free speech.\n\n\nWhereas, Judge Mann has taken\nthat right away from and sentenced\nsome $50 of our fellow workers to\nterms in jail, therefore, be it\n\n\nResolved, That we, the Indus\ntrial Newsboys of Spokane, pledge\nyou our earnest support in the way\nOF money and other little helps. Be\n1t further\n\n\nResolved, That a copy of these\nresolutions be sent to the three\nlocal papers and the Industrial\nWorker. Jack Collier. Chairman (\""
    }
  ]
